Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（ルフィ）『ワンピース』　１０周年！\N（一同）乾杯！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・『Ｓｈａｒｅ　Ｔｈｅ　Ｗｏｒｌｄ』\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:01:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:02:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
